query:
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS contract_clause_values (
  id INT AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
  contractId INT NOT NULL,
  clauseId INT,
  title VARCHAR(255),
  customContent TEXT,
  orderIndex INT DEFAULT 0,
  isIncluded BOOLEAN DEFAULT TRUE,
  createdAt TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
  FOREIGN KEY (contractId) REFERENCES contracts_enhanced(id),
  FOREIGN KEY (clauseId) REFERENCES contract_clauses(id)
);
